inlineContent.text: Includes the predicted parameters, and ways to get a user-visible description
for a predicted or suggested action given those parameters.

abstract.text: Make your app’s content and actions discoverable with system experiences like Spotlight, widgets, and enhanced action capabilities of Siri, powered by Apple Intelligence.
An interface for providing an app-specific capability that people invoke
from system experiences like Siri and the Shortcuts app.
A prediction for a specific app intent that the system might display to someone when it’s relevant.
An interface that provides the configuration for a single prediction.
An interface that allows the system to suggest the app intent to someone in the future using predictions you provide.
